  "body": "Originally reported by @clauxx [here](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/17785#issuecomment-1804254216)\r\n\r\nCurrently the issue has been encountered only on IOS 17.x\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Send a long multiline message (so that composer is maximised) \r\n2. Open editing of this message \r\n3. Start entering text into new line\r\n4. Observe the behaviour\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** When the composer is maximized and you're entering text into the new line, for the first 2-3 characters, the text jumps up and after ~3rd character the cursor/text comes back. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/21865759/74dcc752-002c-45b0-ac83-de2dcb99adaa\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
